{"tid":1598529,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)死侍1-2 狂野時速外傳","createTime":"2019-09-27T13:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T20:01:28.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e02ceac4ca07eb8f4343ffb76937eb592cfa35","tid":1598529,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:32:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHaT%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=e84afa7c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHaT%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=7e75b7e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHaT%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=134eac78\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.itw01.com/images/2018/04/01/02/2413_uLvtC6_VZNSWED.jpg!r1024x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.itw01.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F02%2F2413_uLvtC6_VZNSWED.jpg%21r1024x0.jpg&h=c1edbe40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/3b/Hobbs_&amp;_Shaw_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F3b%2FHobbs_%26_Shaw_Poster.jpg&h=c1d2202c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.前特種部隊傭兵韋德&middot;威爾森退伍後，以臨時打手為業，常收費為人「打抱不平」，但他一直否認自己是一個英雄。一日，他在俱樂部認識一位名叫凡妮莎的脫衣舞娘，和她譜出一段長時間的熱戀，以節日過的親密接觸。當他們倆開始談婚論嫁時，韋德卻被診斷出已經癌症末期，為了不讓深愛的未婚妻難過，韋德只好趁夜裡離她而去，迫切想把癌症治好而四處求醫。一個自稱「史密斯特工」的招募員對韋德提議加入他代表的組織，稱他們的科學技術能夠治療他的病症。韋德輕信他的話而立馬簽約，之後被帶到以阿賈克斯和沙塵天使管理的移動型實驗室，但裡面所進行的非法實驗卻只讓韋德痛苦萬分<br />\n<br />\n2.韋德&middot;威爾森化身「死侍」從事國際僱傭兵度過兩年，在跟他心愛女友凡妮莎的週年紀念日當天，兩人計劃組建一個家庭、生個小孩。然而不久，他們住處遭遇當天韋德沒能殺死成功的一位俄國毒梟帶人前來尋仇，凡妮莎當場中槍身亡，韋德便殺光在場敵人和毒梟本人。之後的六個星期下來，悲痛的韋德開始自怨自艾乃至產生自殺念頭，在住處裡堆滿油桶本想炸死自己，卻因自身能力而還是未成功。他粉碎的身體最後被鋼人拼湊回去痊癒，其將韋德接回X宅邸並命令他接受X戰警的訓練。而韋德對凡妮莎的回憶僅剩一個鉛製的投分球檯遊戲幣，作為凡妮莎死前送他週年紀念禮物<br />\n<br />\n3.軍情六處探員哈蒂&middot;蕭率領一隊人馬，從恐怖組織「伊特昂」手中奪回經編碼的超級病毒「雪花」。體內植入控制組件、擁有超人類能力的「伊特昂」打手布列斯頓&middot;勞勒前來救場。趁著雙方激鬥，哈蒂將病毒植入體內後逃之夭夭，留下她的特工被殺死<br />\n<br />\n9 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHaT%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=0d9bb770\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHaT%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=bba2cdcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1883994cfe7d6032ec7335b9be60b10dd4186847","tid":1598529,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:34:46.000Z","ms